_sText:
One day got bored and decided to make a map
cousins were over and gave ideas.....

Counter Strike - Aim - Orange - One Tower

Map by: Luciano Anastassiou (shield543)

Have fun in my 'Orange Textured' Map.

Terrorists: Spawn on one side of the map. No bomb target.

Counter-Terrorists: Spawn on other side of map. 
No hostages/bombs to take care of.

There is a tower in the middle which, if you are quick,
you can run to and climb the ladder to the top for a
good sniper position.

-------
This map will bot be sold/distributed in any other way other than in-game.
If you wish to make a deal, I can be contacted at: shield543@yahoo.com
If I see this map anywhere else without my permission. Legal action will
take place!!!
